       <div class="item-page"> 
        <h2> <a href="/root/emergency-contact-information.html"> Emergency Contact Information and Procedures</a> </h2> 
        <ul class="actions"> 
         <li class="print-icon"> <a href="/root/emergency-contact-information.html?tmpl=component&amp;print=1&amp;layout=default&amp;page=" title="Print" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','status=no,toolbar=no,scrollbars=yes,titlebar=no,menubar=no,resizable=yes,width=640,height=480,directories=no,location=no'); return false;" rel="nofollow"><img src="/root/media/system/images/printButton.png" alt="Print"></a> </li> 
         <li class="email-icon"> <a href="/root/component/mailto/?tmpl=component&amp;template=tczcbulldogalert&amp;link=88f0949cbc572ae93225db630e5e8c8535ee2678" title="Email" onclick="window.open(this.href,'win2','width=400,height=350,menubar=yes,resizable=yes'); return false;"><img src="/root/media/system/images/emailButton.png" alt="Email"></a> </li> 
        </ul> 
        <hr> 
        <p><img src="http://www.citadel.edu/root/images/Misc/bulldogalert_qr.png" border="0" alt="QR code to open Emergency Contact information on your phone" width="40" style="float: left; margin-right: 15px; margin-top: 3px;"></p> 
        <p style="margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 10px; color: gray;">For your convenience, and so you may quickly access this page on your smart phone, a QR code is available at the bottom of this page.</p> 
        <hr> 
        <p>The Citadel is providing a safe and secure environment to its students, faculty, staff, and visitors through the training of personnel and practice of emergency exercises on campus. In the event of an emergency requiring immediate action and notification of The Citadel community, the following actions will be taken:</p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>emergency sirens will sound</li> 
         <li>the BulldogAlert messaging system will send a combination of text, email, and voice messages to all communication devices and</li> 
         <li>emergency information and instructions will be posted to www.bulldogalert.info</li> 
        </ul> 
        <p>The BulldogAlert messaging system broadcasts emergency information to email addresses and phone numbers provided by students, faculty, and staff. The aforementioned people can update their contact information in <a href="https://portal.blackboardconnected.com/1022805" target="_blank">Blackboard Connect</a> or the <a href="http://lesesnegateway.citadel.edu" target="_blank">Lesesne Gateway</a> portal. This information is kept confidential.</p> 
        <hr> 
        <h3>BulldogAlert</h3> 
        <p>Current information about campus wide emergencies will be posted to the <a href="/root/../">BulldogAlert homepage</a>.</p> 
        <hr> 
