        <hr> 
        <h3>&nbsp;</h3> 
        <h3>Quick Guide for Emergency Procedures</h3> 
        <p>&nbsp;</p> 
        <p class="MsoPlainText">When faced with an emergency listed below, follow the suggested steps.</p> 
        <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Active Shooter on Campus</span></p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>If possible, exit building.</li> 
         <li>If exit is not possible, clear corridor and remain behind locked or barricaded door, close windows/blinds, turn off lights, stay out of view and remain quiet.</li> 
         <li>Notify Public Safety <em>843-953-5114, or 811 (landline use). </em></li> 
        </ul> 
        <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Bomb Threat</span></p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>If threat comes by telephone, get as much information as possible.</li> 
         <li>Notify Public Safety <em>843-953-5114, or 811 (landline use). </em></li> 
        </ul> 
        <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Fire</span></p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>Activate fire alarm.</li> 
         <li>Notify Public Safety <em>843-953-5114, or 811 (landline use). </em></li> 
         <li>Notify others in the building; help those needing assistance.</li> 
         <li>Evacuate the building.</li> 
        </ul> 
        <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Serious Injury/Accident</span></p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>Render immediate first aid.</li> 
         <li>Notify Public Safety <em>843-953-5114, or 811 (landline use). </em></li> 
        </ul> 
        <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Suspicious Package</span></p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>Do not touch package; evacuate immediate area.</li> 
         <li>Notify Public Safety <em>843-953-5114, or 811 (landline use). </em></li> 
        </ul> 
        <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Suspicious Person</span></p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>Do not physically confront or block their exit from a building; do not let person into a locked room.</li> 
         <li>Notify Public Safety <em>843-953-5114, or 811 (landline use). </em></li> 
        </ul> 
        <p><span style="text-decoration: underline;">Tornado</span></p> 
        <ul> 
         <li>Seek refuge in an interior, ground floor hallway or room.</li> 
        </ul> 
        <hr> 
